@SseDemo_HostAddress = http://localhost:5121
@ApiKey = demo-api-key-1

### Health check
GET {{SseDemo_HostAddress}}/health
Accept: application/json

### Connect to SSE stream
GET {{SseDemo_HostAddress}}/api/sse/connect?clientId=test-client
X-API-Key: {{ApiKey}}

### Send notification to all clients
POST {{SseDemo_HostAddress}}/api/sse/notification
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{ApiKey}}

{
  "message": "This is a test notification",
  "severity": "info"
}

### Send alert to all clients
POST {{SseDemo_HostAddress}}/api/sse/alert
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{ApiKey}}

{
  "message": "System maintenance scheduled for midnight",
  "severity": "high",
  "category": "system"
}

### Send critical alert to all clients
POST {{SseDemo_HostAddress}}/api/sse/alert
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{ApiKey}}

{
  "message": "Security breach detected!",
  "severity": "critical",
  "category": "security"
}

### Send data update to all clients
POST {{SseDemo_HostAddress}}/api/sse/data-update
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{ApiKey}}

{
  "entityId": "user-123",
  "entityType": "user",
  "changes": {
    "name": "John Doe",
    "email": "john@example.com"
  }
}

### Broadcast custom event to all clients
POST {{SseDemo_HostAddress}}/api/sse/broadcast
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{ApiKey}}

{
  "eventType": "heartbeat",
  "data": "{\"timestamp\":\"2024-01-01T12:00:00Z\"}"
}

### Start automatic demo events (cycles through all event types)
POST {{SseDemo_HostAddress}}/api/demo/start
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{ApiKey}}

{
  "intervalSeconds": 3
}

### Stop automatic demo events
POST {{SseDemo_HostAddress}}/api/demo/stop
X-API-Key: {{ApiKey}}

### Check demo status
GET {{SseDemo_HostAddress}}/api/demo/status
X-API-Key: {{ApiKey}}